content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Network analytics report in Workbench insights April 14, 2025—Workbench insights now have a insight-level network analytics report. The network analytics report shows network correlations between the objects included in a Workbench insight. The report provides comprehensive analytics to help you monitor, manage, and identify the abnormal network traffic in your environment. Learn more.
